overview:
Jana Janocha is a Brand Marketeer from Germany and moved to the United States in early 2011. She started her own business in 2011, offering marketing consultancy for start-ups in the Silicon Valley.

Earlier in life, Jana worked as a Brand Manager for Telefonica Germany and led national advertising campaigns as well as international cooperation projects.

Jana Janocha attended RFH University in Cologne, Germany and studied media economics with specialization in marketing and communication management.

While at RFH University, Jana volunteered in student council, being responsible for student events and foreign student affairs.
